Honkai Star Rail
            
Honkai: Star Rail is a 2023 free-to-play role-playing gacha video game 
developed and published by miHoYo (with publishing outside mainland China under 
Cognosphere, d/b/a HoYoverse). It is the fourth installment in the Honkai series, 
utilizing some characters from Honkai Impact 3rd and some gameplay elements from Genshin Impact. 
The game features the main character, who is referred to as the Trailblazer, traveling across 
the universe through the Astral Express to help and connect the worlds while involved in 
resolving disasters caused by "Stellarons" and other third parties.

